sentences.zh: 昔詩書述虞夏之際，舜禹受襢，積德累功，洽於百姓，攝位行政，考之于天，經數十年，然後在位。

translations.literal: Former Poetry Documents narrated Yu Xia between, Shun Yu received mantle, accumulated virtue piled merit, harmonized at common people, assumed position administered government, tested it at heaven, passed several decades, then was in position.
translations.idiomatic: Formerly the Poetry and Documents narrated the time between Yu and Xia, when Shun and Yu received the mantle, accumulated virtue and piled merit, harmonized with the common people, assumed position and administered government, tested it by heaven, passed several decades, and then was in position.

sentences.zh: 殷周之王，乃繇镨稷，修仁行義，歷十餘世，至于湯武，然後放殺。

translations.literal: Yin Zhou kings, then followed Hou Ji, cultivated benevolence practiced righteousness, passed ten more generations, arrived at Tang Wu, then banished killed.
translations.idiomatic: The kings of Yin and Zhou then followed Hou Ji, cultivated benevolence and practiced righteousness, passed through more than ten generations, arrived at Tang and Wu, and then banished and killed.

sentences.zh: 秦起襄公，章文、繆，獻、孝、昭、嚴，稍蠶食六國，百有餘載，至始皇，乃并天下。

translations.literal: Qin arose Xianggong, Zhang Wen, Mu, Xian, Xiao, Zhao, Yan, gradually silkworm ate six states, hundred and more years, arrived at Shihuang, then united empire.
translations.idiomatic: Qin arose with Xianggong, then Zhang, Wen, Mu, Xian, Xiao, Zhao, Yan, gradually nibbling away at the six states over more than a hundred years, until Shihuang, who then united the empire.

sentences.zh: 以德若彼，用力如此其艱難也。

translations.literal: Used virtue like that, employed strength thus so its difficult also.
translations.idiomatic: Using virtue like that, employing strength thus so difficult.

sentences.zh: 秦既稱帝，患周之敗，以為起於處士橫議，諸侯力爭，四夷交侵，以弱見奪。

translations.literal: Qin already called emperor, worried Zhou defeat, considered arose from reclusive scholars transverse discussions, feudal lords force contended, four barbarians mutually invaded, with weakness seen seized.
translations.idiomatic: Qin having already called himself emperor, worried about Zhou's defeat, considered it arose from reclusive scholars' transverse discussions, feudal lords' forceful contention, four barbarians mutually invading, and being seized when weak.

sentences.zh: 於是削去五等，墮城銷刃，箝語燒書，內鋤雄俊，外攘胡粵，用壹威權，為萬世安。

translations.literal: Thereupon pared away five ranks, destroyed walls melted blades, clamped speech burned books, inner hoed heroic outstanding, outer expelled Hu Yue, used unified awe authority, for ten thousand generations peace.
translations.idiomatic: Thereupon pared away the five ranks, destroyed walls and melted blades, clamped speech and burned books, hoed out heroic and outstanding within, expelled Hu and Yue without, used unified awe and authority, for ten thousand generations' peace.

sentences.zh: 然十餘年間，猛敵橫發乎不虞，適戍彊於五伯，閭閻偪於戎狄，嚮應钇於謗議，奮臂威於甲兵。

translations.literal: However ten more years between, fierce enemies horizontal arose unexpectedly, just garrisoned strong at five hegemons, alleys pressed by Rong Di, faced responded gathered at slander discussions, exerted arms awed at armored troops.
translations.idiomatic: However within more than ten years, fierce enemies arose unexpectedly, just garrisoned strongly at the five hegemons, alleys pressed by Rong and Di, faced and responded gathered at slanderous discussions, exerted arms and awed with armored troops.

sentences.zh: 鄉秦之禁，適所以資豪桀而速自斃也。

translations.literal: Direction Qin prohibitions, just what provided heroic outstanding and hastened self destruction also.
translations.idiomatic: Qin's prohibitions just provided for heroic and outstanding men and hastened self-destruction.

sentences.zh: 是以漢亡尺土之階，繇一劍之任，五載而成帝業。

translations.literal: Therefore Han perished foot soil steps, followed one sword commission, five years and completed emperor enterprise.
translations.idiomatic: Therefore Han, without even a foot of soil as steps, followed one sword's commission, and in five years completed the emperor's enterprise.

translations.literal: Documents traditions what recorded, not once had there.
translations.idiomatic: What the Documents and traditions record, never once had there.

translations.literal: What then?
translations.idiomatic: What then?

sentences.zh: 古世相革，皆承聖王之烈，今漢獨收孤秦之弊。

translations.literal: Ancient generations mutually changed, all inherited sage kings achievements, now Han alone received isolated Qin faults.
translations.idiomatic: Ancient generations mutually changed, all inherited sage kings' achievements, now Han alone received isolated Qin's faults.

sentences.zh: 鐫金石者難為功，摧枯朽者易為力，其固然也。

translations.literal: Carved metal stone ones difficult made merit, destroyed withered rotten ones easy made strength, its clear also.
translations.idiomatic: Those who carved metal and stone found it difficult to make merit, those who destroyed withered and rotten found it easy to make strength—it is clear.

sentences.zh: 故據漢受命，譜十八王，月而列之，天下一統，乃以年數。

translations.literal: Therefore according Han received mandate, tabled eighteen kings, month and listed them, empire unified, then used year numbers.
translations.idiomatic: Therefore according to Han receiving the mandate, tabled the eighteen kings, listed them by month, the empire unified, then used year numbers.

cells.content: 不疑薨，諡曰哀，無子。十月癸丑，王義始，故襄城候。

cells.idiomatic: Buyi passed away, posthumous name Ai, no sons. Tenth month, gui chou: King Yi began, former Xiangcheng marquis.

cells.idiomatic: Tai passed away, posthumous name Su. Son Jia succeeded as king.
